Subject: Secunia Research: Lotus Notes Folio Flat File
	Parsing Buffer	Overflows

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 08/04/2008

       - Lotus Notes Folio Flat File Parsing Buffer Overflows -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

Affected Software....................................................1
Severity.............................................................2
